<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَيَسْأَلُونَكَ عَنِ الْجِبَالِ , فَقُلْ يَنْسِفُهَا رَبِّي نَسْفًا , فَيَذَرُهَا قَاعًا صَفْصَفًا , لَا تَرَى فِيهَا عِوَجًا وَلَا أَمْتًا}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٩٥:</span> <span class="c3">{قَاعًا}</span>: يَعْلُوهُ المَاءُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَالصَّفْصَفُ:</span> المُسْتَوِي مِنَ الأَرْضِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{عِوَجًا}</span>: وَادِيًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{وَلَا أَمْتًا}</span>: رَابِيَةً.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [طه: ١٠٥ - ١٠٧]</p> </div>